nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 176 is the 154th issue of the Star Wars Insider magazine and the eighty-fourth issue published by Titan Magazines. It was released on October 17, 2017. It provided coverage for the cast and crew for Star Wars Rebels, John Williams, various Star Wars fans across the world, coverage of various theatrical trailers, Daisy Ridley, various heroines in the saga, and matte paintings.
Features the very best interviews and articles about the greatest space adventure of all time! Discover amazing features you never knew! Insider is the ultimate guide to the timeless saga!
